Tony Bennett says he&rsquo;d love to collaborate with Lady Gaga again in new Twitter Q&amp;A:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I love working with &lsquo;Lady&rsquo; so anytime she wants to sing live or in the studio I am always ready.&rdquo;

In a now-deleted tweet, The Weeknd seems to have announced new music coming out tomorrow night.<br />
<br />
&quot;a few lullaby's tomorrow night&quot;

Dua Lipa expressed interest in joining the cast of #AHS:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I&rsquo;d really like to be on American Horror Story. Ive always loved the characters in that series &amp; how they get to play so many different roles with every season &amp; I just love the stories behind it. I&rsquo;ve always been a fan&rdquo;

Lady Gaga&rsquo;s &lsquo;Chromatica&rsquo; is described as a return to the singer&rsquo;s &ldquo;purest pop form&rdquo; in new InStyle profile: <br />
<br />
&ldquo;It&rsquo;s as if long-lost tracks from the &lsquo;Paparazzi&rsquo; era had just been found, polished up and newly released.&rdquo;

Lady Gaga praises Taylor Swift during her &lsquo;One World: Together At Home&rsquo; performance of &ldquo;Soon You&rsquo;ll Get Better&rdquo;:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;This is so beautiful, Taylor. Thank you for sharing this vulnerable moment with us.&rdquo;

Lady Gaga showed love to Shawn Mendes &amp; Camila Cabello during their &lsquo;Together At Home&rsquo;&nbsp;performance.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I love you two so much. You&rsquo;re beautiful! Thank you so much, mwah!&rdquo;

Adele&rsquo;s makeup artist, Michael Ashton has revealed on his Instagram story that something is coming soon.<br />
<br />
&quot;Exciting news coming soon!! Get ready to get on board&rdquo;

G-Eazy references his past relationship with Lana Del Rey on his new collaboration, &quot;Moana&quot;:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I know a Keisha and I know Lana, they try to get me back, but I'm like, &lsquo;No, nah, nah&rsquo;.&rdquo;

Camila Cabello praises Dua Lipa&rsquo;s &lsquo;Future Nostalgia&rsquo; on Instagram:<br />
<br />
&ldquo;This album is amazing @dualipa ! so fresh yet it satisfies my pop music heart !!!!!&rdquo;

